6. Atlas — Knowledge Navigation Layer

The Pantheon Atlas maps artifact relationships.

Nodes = artifacts
Edges = dependencies / translations / reuse

Example structure:

Artifact A → depends on → Artifact B
Artifact C → extends → Artifact B
Artifact D → translates → Artifact A


